          "chapter": null,
          "text": "Anybody whose mind is proud enough not to breed true, secretly carries a bomb at the back of his brain; ",
          "sentence": "Anybody whose mind is proud enough not to breed true, secretly carries a bomb at the back of his brain; and so I suggest, just for the fun of the thing, taking that private bomb and carefully dropping it upon the model city of commonsense. ",
