          "chapter": null,
          "text": " It is impersonal imagination and artistic delight. ",
          "sentence": "So what is the authentic instrument to be used by the reader? It is impersonal imagination and artistic delight. What should be established, I think, is an artistic harmonious balance between the reader's mind and the author’s mind. ",
